@DATABASE "Thrust"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - T - Thrust"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - T
                   ====================================

                                  Thrust
                                  ======



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" rxs "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(39219,0)"}          39219,0
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(39297,255)"}          39297,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
